*{{cite web|title=Fourteenth Annual Youth in Film Awards 1991-1992|url=http://www.youngartistawards.org/pastnoms14.htm|publisher=The Young Artist Foundation|accessdate=15 August 2011|postscript=. won|archive-date=2011-03-04|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5ww3Qlhws?url=http://www.youngartistawards.org/pastnoms14.htm|dead-url=no}}
*{{cite web|title=Fifteenth Annual Youth in Film Awards 1992-1993|url=http://www.youngartistawards.org/pastnoms15.htm|publisher=The Young Artist Foundation|accessdate=15 August 2011|postscript=. nominated|archive-date=2000-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20000709095207/http://www.youngartistawards.org/pastnoms15.htm|dead-url=no}}
*{{cite web|title=Sixteenth Annual Youth in Film Awards 1993-1994|url=http://www.youngartistawards.org/pastnoms16.htm|publisher=The Young Artist Foundation|accessdate=15 August 2011|postscript=. won|archive-date=2010-10-22|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5texRaYrJ?url=http://www.youngartistawards.org/pastnoms16.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 該角色也讓梅莉莎在FMV電玩遊戲「尼克羅頓公司實驗室」(Nickelodeon's Director's Lab)參與一角，擔任一個導遊帶領玩家走訪電影片廠。1992年，梅莉莎和劇組的成員[[Jason_Zimbler|Jason Zimbler]]一同參加遊戲節目[[Nick_Arcade_(game_show)|Nick Arcade]]。 該節目其中一個挑戰單元[[Sonic_The_Hedgehog_2|Sonic The Hedgehog 2]]，梅莉莎是少數參加該單元的基礎挑戰的人。{{Citation needed|date=February 2011}}

杭特也以Clarissa的名義錄製過兩張專輯，「This is What 'Na Na' Means」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.amazon.com/This-What-Na-Means/dp/B000008MYZ |title=This is What "Na Na" Means: Clarissa & the |publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=June 23, 2010 |archive-date=2012-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120104042126/http://www.amazon.com/This-What-Na-Means/dp/B000008MYZ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 和[[Peter_and_the_Wolf|Peter and the Wolf]]‧<ref>[http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/prokofiev-peter-wolf-saint/id264301779 Prokofiev: Peter and the Wolf - Saint-Saëns: Carnival of the Animals - Britten: Young Person's Guide to the Orchestra] {{Wayback|url=http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/prokofiev-peter-wolf-saint/id264301779 |date=20121111070808 }}, on iTunes</ref>

