梅莉莎也曾在1991年在尼克羅頓公司製播的影集[[Are_You_Afraid_of_the_Dark?|Are You Afraid of the Dark?]]，第二季中一集"The Tale Of The Frozen Ghost"現身。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.netflix.com/Movie/Are-You-Afraid-of-the-Dark-Freaky-Favorites/70055708 |title=Are You Afraid of the Dark? Freaky Favorites |publisher=Netflix.com |accessdate=November 4, 2010 |archive-date=2012-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112031353/http://www.netflix.com/Movie/Are-You-Afraid-of-the-Dark-Freaky-Favorites/70055708 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===魔法少女薩琳娜時期（1995{{ndash}}2003）===
在知名影集結束之後，梅莉莎進入[[紐約大學|紐約大學]]念書。<ref>{{cite news |last=Jacobs |first=A.J |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,294744,00.html |title=Behind the scenes of ''Sabrina'' -- Nickelodeon alum Melissa Joan Hart casts a spell on prime time |publisher=Entertainment Weekly |date=October 25, 1996 |accessdate=February 22, 2011 |archive-date=2012-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020230915/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,294744,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>但是她並沒有完成學位。因為她主演1996年的一部電影[[魔法少女薩琳娜(電影)|魔法少女薩琳娜]]。<ref>{{cite news |last=Marriott |first=Michel |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/162875/Sabrina-the-Teenage-Witch/overview |title=Sabrina the Teenage Witch - Trailer - Cast - Showtimes - NYTimes.com |publisher=Movies.nytimes.com |date= |accessdate=June 23, 2010 |archive-date=2012-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103191750/http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/162875/Sabrina-the-Teenage-Witch/overview |dead-url=no }}</ref> 該部電影是同名的知名電視影集改編而成(該部影集在CBS電視台和WB電視台連續播放七季)。<ref name="pqasb.pqarchiver.com">{{cite news |url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/sptimes/access/22721836.html?dids=22721836:22721836&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=May+13%2C+1996&author=HELEN+A.S.+POPKIN&pub=St.+Petersburg+Times&desc=Melissa+explains+it+all+Series%3A+Xpress&pqatl=google |title=Melissa explains it all Series: Xpress |publisher=Pqasb.pqarchiver.com |date=May 13, 1996 |accessdate=June 23, 2010 |first=Helen A.S. |last=Popkin }}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref name="tv.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.tv.com/sabrina-the-teenage-witch/show/50/summary.html |title=Sabrina, the Teenage Witch on |publisher=Tv.com |date= |accessdate=June 23, 2010 |archive-date=2011-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110821233810/http://www.tv.com/sabrina-the-teenage-witch/show/50/summary.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>之後梅莉莎又參與該部電影的卡通版本，替該部卡通的海爾達姑姑和琪爾達姑姑配音。梅莉莎的妹妹[[Emily_Hart|Emily Hart]]也參與其中主角的配音工作。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tv.com/sabrina-the-animated-series/show/1536/cast.html?tag=page_nav;subtabs;cast |title=Sabrina the Animated Series Cast and Crew on |publisher=Tv.com |date= |accessdate=June 23, 2010 |archive-date=2012-09-18 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120918030624/http://www.tv.com/sabrina-the-animated-series/show/1536/cast.html?tag=page_nav;subtabs;cast |dead-url=no }}</ref> 而在同時，她也擔任影集[[Touched_by_an_Angel|Touched by an Angel]]的特別嘉賓，並且主演許多電視電影。

到了1998年，梅莉莎飾演電影[[Can't_Hardly_Wait|Can't Hardly Wait]]的其中一個小角色，<ref name="reelviews.net Can't Hardly Wait">{{cite web |url=http://www.reelviews.net/movies/c/cant_wait.html |title=Review: Can't Hardly Wait |publisher=reelviews.net |first=James |last=Berardinelli |date=June 12, 1998 |accessdate=October 23, 2010 |archive-date=2012-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324112950/http://www.reelviews.net/movies/c/cant_wait.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>之後主演電影[[Drive_Me_Crazy|Next to You]]，與[[Adrian_Grenier|Adrian Grenier]]共同擔綱演出。<ref name="foxmovies.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.foxmovies.com/drivemecrazy/ |title=Drive Me Crazy |publisher=Foxmovies.com |date=August 31, 1999 |accessdate=June 23, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091027215340/http://www.foxmovies.com/drivemecrazy/ |archivedate=2009年10月27日 }}</ref>梅莉莎邀請她的朋友[[布蘭妮|布蘭妮]] 一同演唱[[(You_Drive_Me)_Crazy|(You Drive Me) Crazy]]的[[混音|混音]]版本並收錄到該電影的電影原聲帶中。為了成功的讓該首單曲打入[[告示牌百強單曲榜|告示牌百強單曲榜]]，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/britney-spears/chart-history/290150#/song/britney-spears/you-drive-me-crazy/1567777 |title=Britney Spears Album & Song Chart History |publisher=Billboard.com |date= |accessdate=June 23, 2010 |archive-date=2012-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118021116/http://www.billboard.com/artist/britney-spears/chart-history/290150#/song/britney-spears/you-drive-me-crazy/1567777 |dead-url=no }}</ref>電影的名稱改成[[Drive_Me_Crazy|Drive Me Crazy]]並讓梅莉莎加入該單曲的音樂錄影帶當中演出。<ref>{{cite web |last=Vena |first=Jocelyn |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1626386/20091116/spears_britney.jhtml |title=Britney Spears Wanted '(You Drive Me) Crazy' Video To Take Her 'To The Next Level' - News Story | Music, Celebrity, Artist News | MTV News |publisher=Mtv.com |date=November 16, 2009 |accessdate=June 23, 2010 |archive-date=2010-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101003195954/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1626386/20091116/spears_britney.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在此同時，布蘭妮也在[[魔法少女薩琳娜(影集)|魔法少女薩琳娜]]該部影集中擔任特別嘉賓，飾演她自己。

梅莉莎在1999年十月份的男性雜誌[[Maxim_magazine|Maxim]]上出現一系列的貼身性感照片。<ref name="maxim.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.maxim.com/girls/girls-of-maxim/44718/melissa-joan-hart.html |title=Melissa Joan Hart Pictures - 1 of 4 - Maxim Girls Photo Gallery |publisher=Maxim.com |date= |accessdate=June 23, 2010 |archive-date=2010-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101024161539/http://www.maxim.com/girls/girls-of-maxim/44718/melissa-joan-hart.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>梅莉莎一直持續她的演員生涯直到2000年，包括一部電影''Rent Control''，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://videoeta.com/movie/51969 |title=Rent Control (2002) - Melissa Joan Hart, Carmen Electra, Ryan Browning |publisher=Videoeta.com |date= |accessdate=June 23, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722010854/http://videoeta.com/movie/51969 |archivedate=2011年7月22日 }}</ref> 該部電影在2005年於[[ABC_Family|ABC Family]]電視台上映。梅莉莎也繼續在[[魔法少女薩琳娜|魔法少女薩琳娜]]演出，直到該部戲在2003年結束。<ref name="tv.com"/>並且幫許多動畫配音。

1999年，梅莉莎首次執導一部她妹妹[[Emily_Hart|Emily Hart]]主演的[[迪士尼頻道|迪士尼頻道]]的影集[[So_Weird|So Weird]]中的一集"Snapshot"。2001年又幫尼克羅頓電視公司的另一部影集[[Taina_(TV_series)|Taina]]中執導一集。在2001到2002年，梅莉莎執導''魔法少女薩琳娜''的其中六集，包括第六季的最後一集。{{Citation needed|date=February 2011}}

===後薩琳娜時期（2004{{ndash}}現今）===
[[File:Melissa_Joan_Hart_at_Paley_Center.jpg|thumb]]
結束''魔法少女薩琳娜''之後，梅莉莎開始直到她的第一部電影，一部15分鐘的實境短片「無聲」(''Mute'')(2005)，由她妹妹Emily主演。
